CONVERSATION TITLE: Nail Test Engineering Interviews with 150+ FAANG Instructors
CONTENT:
Dear Hunter,


Interview Kickstart is the most effective Tech Interview Prep Program in the US. Our 500+ FAANG instructors have helped over 15,000 engineers get offers from Top Tier-1 companies.


Our Test Engineering interview prep course is designed by Test Engineers from FAANG companies and includes:


  1. Live classes focusing on the Test Engineering Domain starting from fundamentals and then covering topics like API Testing, Performance Testing, Automation Testing, and Test Design Patterns.
  2. Practice problems and assignments along the lines of actual interview question preparing you for actual interviews.
  3. Mock Test Engineering Interviews & career guidance


Learn more about our program in our free 60-minute webinar, which will cover:


  • Our tried & tested strategy for cracking Top Tier 1 tech interviews
  • How Top Tier 1 companies hiring process works (from FAANG hiring managers)
  • The 4 areas you must prepare for before your interview
  • How you can accelerate your learning with the help of FAANG instructors

Hi Hunter,

 

At National University, we believe everyone deserves the opportunity to experience the fulfillment of personal and professional achievement that a college degree may bring. Our Key Grant is designed to remove financial barriers to earning a high-quality college degree for prospective students in underserved populations.

 

How it Works


The NU Key Grant offers a needs-based 50% tuition reduction that opens the door to higher education for qualified students who may not be able to afford a college degree any other way. Whether you are:


  • A first-generation student seeking the American dream
  • Living in an underserved community without access to educational opportunities
  • An enlisted servicemember looking to maximize your education benefit
  • A degree holder hoping to advance your education without Title IV funding

 

National University’s Key Grant is designed to unlock the barrier to your education, the door to your dreams, the pathway to your future.


Applications must be submitted by December 31, 2022.


Sincerely,

 

National University Admissions
